== {{ill|Month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}} of Koushin ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|庚}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙}}), the month of {{ill|March|ja|3月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}} of {{ill|Koushin|ja|庚辰}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明}} until the day before {{ill|Beginning of Summer|ja|立夏}}) as applicable.

== {{ill|Day|ja|日}} of Koushin ==
* {{ill|Emperor Jimmu|ja|神武天皇}} (the founder and first {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇}} of {{ill|Japan|ja|日本}})'s birthday.

=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of {{ill|Koushin|ja|庚辰}} is the 3rd day of {{ill|Hando|ja|犯土|lt=Small Earth|lt_ja=小土}}.


