{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Metal Dragon|kanji=庚辰|romaji=kanoe tatsu|onyomi=kōshin|p=gēngchén|w=keng-ch'en|mi=kɤŋ⁵³ ʈ͡ʂʰən|y=geng1 san4|j=geng1 san4|ci=kɪŋ sɐn|mc=kæŋ ɖin|oc-bs=kˤraŋ ɖiŋ}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}
'''Yang Metal Dragon also known as 庚辰''' (kanoetatsu, koukinnotatsu, koushin) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

It is the 17th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Kibou|ja|己卯|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Shinshi|ja|辛巳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|金|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Dragon|ja|辰|1=Dragon (zodiac)|lt=Dragon (辰)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, establishing a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=相生|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (i.e. Earth generates Metal).

== {{ill|Years of Koushin|ja|庚辰の年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 20 when divided by 60 is a year of {{ill|Koushin|ja|庚辰|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ({{ill|year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}).
