== {{ill|Month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of Koushin ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|March|ja|3月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of {{ill|Koushin|ja|庚辰|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Beginning of Summer|ja|立夏|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) as applicable.

== {{ill|Day|ja|日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of Koushin ==
* {{ill|Emperor Jimmu|ja|神武天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (the founder and first {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of {{ill|Japan|ja|日本|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}})'s birthday.

=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of {{ill|Koushin|ja|庚辰|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is the 3rd day of {{ill|Hando|ja|犯土|lt=Small Earth|lt_ja=小土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.

