It is the 17th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Kibou|ja|己卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Shinshi|ja|辛巳|1=Yin Metal Snake|2=ja|3=辛巳|4=zh|5=辛巳|6=ko|7=신사 (간지)|lt_ko=신사|8=fr|9=Serpent de métal|10=de|11=Metall-Schlange|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|金|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Dragon|ja|辰|1=Dragon (zodiac)|lt=Dragon (辰)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, establishing a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=相生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) (i.e. Earth generates Metal).

== {{ill|Years of Koushin|ja|庚辰の年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ==
