== {{ill|Month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Month (calendar)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Month (calendar)|qq=}} of Koushin ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|lt=Kanoe (庚)|2=ja|3=庚|4=zh|5=庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (庚)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (庚)|qq=}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|lt=Kinoto (乙)|2=ja|3=乙|4=zh|5=乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|March|ja|3月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March|qq=}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}} of {{ill|Koushin|ja|1=Yang Metal Dragon|2=ja|庚辰|1=Yang Metal Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koushin|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koushin|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Metal Dragon|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qingming|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qingming|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Beginning of Summer|ja|立夏|1=Lixia|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Summer|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Summer|13=User:Immanuelle/Lixia|qq=}}) as applicable.

